
Ranger Help for: teach
======================

SYNTAX:      teach follower to <task>
USAGE:       Any terrain
BASE SP:     10 sp

SUMMARY:    
This command allows a Ranger to teach his or her follower to do a
task. Whether or not a Ranger can teach the follower s certain
task is based on how smart the follower is and how many tasks
the follower already knows. Teachable tasks are:
 
Easy Tasks:      fight, carry and guard
Medium Tasks:    hide, fetch and deliver
Difficult Tasks: spy, scout and forage

============================================================================
SEE ALSO: seek, fight, carry, guard, hide, fetch, deliver, spy, scout and
          forage

